'''开放式基金'''（{{lang-en|Open-end fund}}）是一类[[证券投资基金|证券投资基金]]，它可以在任何时候发行（{{lang|en|issue}}）和赎回（{{lang|en|redeem}}）任意数量的基金数额。投资者通常直接从基金發行商处直接购买，而非已有的基金持有人。该概念与封闭式基金相对应（{{lang|en|closed-end fund}}），后者通常一次性发行全部份额，然后允许份额在投资者之间进行交易。<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/05/difference-btween-mutual-funds-and-etfs.html | title = Many investors don’t know the difference between mutual funds and ETFs — here’s why it matters | work = CNBC | date = 2018-10-05 | accessdate = 2021-01-30 | archive-date = 2022-02-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220201190046/https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/05/difference-btween-mutual-funds-and-etfs.html }}</ref>

